      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it is in stunning condition. This beauty has been garaged and pampered since day one\u2014it truly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! There isn't a scratch on it, and the interior is still fresh and flawless. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
