    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system in peak operational state. This vehicle boasts a reinforced rear subframe and has undergone a comprehensive rod bearing replacement for long-term mechanical reliability. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, delivering power through a pristine M-Variable limited-slip differential. Every bushing, seal, and fluid is current, ensuring the chassis dynamics remain as sharp as the day it left Regensburg. Flawless aesthetics meet rigorous mechanical standards in this collector-tier example.",
      "price": 46500.0,
