    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies the most discerning automotive enthusiast. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and reflects a level of care rarely seen on the secondary market. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine without a single stone chip, swirl mark, or blemish across the entire body. All glass is original and crystal clear, and the factory alloy wheels are in pristine condition with no curb rash or pitting. Step inside to an interior that remains in 'time capsule' condition; the premium leather seating surfaces are supple and free of any bolsters wear or creasing, while the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every technological feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance suite, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative. It comes with a complete, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians, ensuring the powertrain is as responsive and smooth as the day it was manufactured. This is a smoke-free, pet-free, single-owner vehicle that represents the pinnacle of its class. We welcome independent inspections to confirm its impeccable status.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
