    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously gotta see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I've babied this car since day one! You won't find a single scratch, and the interior is absolutely pristine. It still has that new-car smell and drives like an absolute dream. I'm really sad to let it go, but I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Drop me a message and come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
