    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is an exceptional E46 M3, representing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS to deliver a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox to an M Variable Differential Lock. Mechanically, this chassis is superlative; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the VANOS system has been fully overhauled to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the interior remains free of bolster wear or UV degradation. Every bushing, gasket, and fluid has been maintained to factory specifications, resulting in a tight, communicative driving experience devoid of NVH issues. This is a turnkey investment-grade specimen for the purist.",
